{"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/Index","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQs"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Learn how to use our built-in parental gate for apps ‚ÄòMade for Kids‚Äô to comply with Apples guidelines and avoid accidental purchases by small children.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"FAQs","title":"Are ‚ÄòMade for Kids‚Äô apps supported with a Parental Gate?"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-ParentalGate"},"kind":"article","seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-HowItWorks","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-Privacy","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-Validation","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-Pricing","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-MigrateFromRevenueCat","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-MigrateFromPaidUpFront","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-ServerLimits"],"generated":true}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Short-Answer","text":"Short Answer","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes, the FreemiumKit SDK ships with a built-in parental gate. Just call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FreemiumKit.shared.enableParentalGate(options:)"},{"text":" upon app start.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Full-Answer","text":"Full Answer","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We‚Äôve built a simple math-based parental gate that will ask a random multiplication question with numbers from 2 to 10. This should be easy enough for any parent to solve, but tricky enough to avoid small children (6 or younger) accidentally getting into the paywall, as required by the "},{"type":"reference","identifi